---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Cenník 2026"
permalink: /cennik/
---
<header class="header header--inner">
  <div class="text-box">
    <h1 class="heading-primary">
      <span class="heading-primary-main">Cenník 2026</span>
    </h1>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="page-content">
  <h1>Cenník 2026</h1>

  <p>
    <strong>Hlavná sezóna:</strong> {{ pricing.season_start }} – {{ pricing.season_end }}<br>
    {{ pricing.open_hours_note }}
  </p>

  <div class="pricing-section">
    <div class="pricing-section__title">Otváracie hodiny recepcie</div>
    <table class="pricing-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Deň</th><th>Hodiny</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for h in pricing.reception_hours %}
        <tr><td>{{ h.day }}</td><td>{{ h.hours }}</td></tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p style="font-size:1.4rem;color:#888;margin-top:1rem;">{{ pricing.off_season_note }}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pricing-section">
    <div class="pricing-section__title">Green Fee</div>
    <table class="pricing-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Typ hry</th><th>Cena</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for item in pricing.green_fees %}
        <tr><td>{{ item.item }}</td><td>{{ item.price }}</td></tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="pricing-section">
    <div class="pricing-section__title">Voučery</div>
    <table class="pricing-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Voučer</th><th>Cena</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for v in pricing.vouchers %}
        <tr><td>{{ v.item }}</td><td>{{ v.price }}</td></tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p style="font-size:1.4rem;color:#555;margin-top:1rem;">
      Voučery je možné zakúpiť počas otváracích hodín recepcie.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="pricing-section">
    <div class="pricing-section__title">Spôsoby platby</div>
    <ul>
      {% for m in pricing.payment_methods %}
      <li>{{ m }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="qr-block mt-4">
    <img
      src="{{ pricing.qr_image }}"
      alt="QR kód — 18 EUR / 9 jamiek 2026"
      class="qr-block__img"
      loading="lazy"
    >
    <div>
      <p><strong>QR kód pre internet banking</strong></p>
      <p>Naskenujte kód pred hrou a uhraďte green fee 18,- EUR / 9 jamiek priamo cez svoju bankovú appku.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;font-size:1.4rem;color:#555;">
        Platobný účet prevádzky ihriska:<br>
        <strong>GM-Golf s.r.o.</strong><br>
        Tatra banka — č.ú. {{ site.bank_prevadzka }}
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="mt-4">Členské príspevky</h2>
  <p>Podrobnosti o členských príspevkoch a výhodách nájdete na stránke <a href="/gk-meander/">GK Meander</a>.</p>

  <h2>Tréningy a zelené karty</h2>
  <p>Ceny tréningov a kurzov nájdete na stránke <a href="/info-blok/treningy-zelene-karty/">Tréningy a zelené karty</a>.</p>
</div>
